s://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/231839_f67bc9f007440c7e977a986739423fdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F231839_f67bc9f007440c7e977a986739423fdb.jpg&h=61880e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/230700_e300c9bf4041e3e004d5ecca91bf14bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F230700_e300c9bf4041e3e004d5ecca91bf14bb.jpg&h=88cbb17c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑魚子<br />\n<br />\n為了主廚王國收藏的禁幣眼鏡，帶領軍團四獸士前去控制國家<br />\n究極武装 可以硬化，軟化，氣體化<br />\n<br />\n銀魚哥哥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n銀魚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/231326_6db22fc88fd867697842ce53b582e49e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F231326_6db22fc88fd867697842ce53b582e49e.jpg&h=d4065594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時是小學生模樣，可變身黑斗蓬男人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/230905_5d60f45821f887623b24d5914e000010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F230905_5d60f45821f887623b24d5914e000010.jpg&h=1126c352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而究極形態可不斷再生，時限三日，以此打敗過漢堡與10倍力量的T骨扒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/231310_d0ddcae94e1deb2dcd920efe7a26d0cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F231310_d0ddcae94e1deb2dcd920efe7a26d0cf.jpg&h=3cb720e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亦有女裝身份沙丁魚出場過<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/230924_a5d4b86faa88b1fa281845a20bba327a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F230924_a5d4b86faa88b1fa281845a20bba327a.png&h=0ce308bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDr.鵝肝<br />\n<br />\n發明禁幣探測眼鏡，一場意外以為兩個仔死了，大受打擊而錯亂，立志消滅所有貯金戰士<br />\n化身BB7另一身份，借助比薩斜塔引無數貯金戰士入內<br />\n<br />\n最後與兒子銀魚對決，兩人死亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/231037_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F231037_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg&h=79640d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/230713_d6e22e3ddcc08c094f640cca9e3bb43a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F230713_d6e22e3ddcc08c094f640cca9e3bb43a.jpg&h=4fafdd4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n芝士火鍋<br />\n<br />\n漢堡徒弟<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/231622_733bffffb96a93fd975067a0b2f48033.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F231622_733bffffb96a93fd975067a0b2f48033.gif&h=cada71f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nT骨扒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/231437_5a4ad7ded40d91d807312018aa5e709c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F231437_5a4ad7ded40d91d807312018aa5e709c.jpg&h=17518256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/231444_32a03ccfe376e30cb0a7f869918353e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F231444_32a03ccfe376e30cb0a7f869918353e8.jpg&h=5f5d3639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看見圓月時能變身為小狗，力量增強十倍。<br />\n看見日蝕時會變身為松鼠，能力比小狗強。<br />\n看見流星則變成大象，比平常弱很多。<br />\n    <br />\n忌廉冷湯家<br />\n來自外星，想要利用黑禁幣消滅地球，與漢堡，芋頭大戰，芋頭及時喚出貯金王，將他們封印至比薩斜塔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/232311_ad8dde88046529caf81e750fb5da1f7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F232311_ad8dde88046529caf81e750fb5da1f7c.jpg&h=379d8cda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99703e1d858b8a436d22b756aef3452846918d76","tid":524174,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"睇唔慣大陸譯名, 又金幣又可樂小子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04774c5c207251dc29974429eb20ae6a0ddbc9a","tid":524174,"uid":31002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:59:40.000Z","msg":"屌明明細個睇到識背，宜家淨係記得啲招名同gba隻game，啲情節唔撚記得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0f778ce019ab2053cee2dc1341f9793bbf9086","tid":524174,"uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:02:41.000Z","msg":"兒童向版hunter"},{"pid":"eaf2f3cd33d0fb330a975ab18825ef403e5dc936","tid":524174,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"劇情暴走 好睇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw隻野有檸檬水dna?<br />\n玩手槍"},{"pid":"13710001604ae93e6b049a0638e0f536eaca8326","tid":524174,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d79f3b0f583004e681d244584f5a42b5b5a88ffe","tid":524174,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e117f53a3626da02c233a9831d94c7d137e7feaa","tid":524174,"uid":102589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"希丁普林  奶油燴飯  <br />\n仲有隻貓  唔記得叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:19:48.000Z","msg":"t骨扒先勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:08:22.000Z